'''
Documentation
This bot connects to the 'Parker_D_bot_lab_server' on discord
This bot responds to questions about the weather specifically
"What is the weather in Charlottesville" (or any other city you choose)
"Is it windy in Charlottesville"
"When is the sunset today in Charlottesville"

This bot gathers this information from openweathermap.org API which provides information about weather in cities worldwide
A series of functions address each aforementioned question and prepare a response for the discord bot to send
The discord bot connects to the server and using on_message() it reacts to messages in the server. Using a series of if then statements, the proper response is sent to the user's question

'''
